"content": "<h2>The ex-consul who ruled the Roman province of Asia was a proconsul</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:38\">ACT 19:38</a></p>\n<h2>The governor of a Roman senatorial province was a proconsul</h2>\n<h3>The proconsul of the province of Cyprus</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:7-Acts13:8\">ACT 13:7–13:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:12\">ACT 13:12</a></p>\n<h3>The proconsul of the province of Achaia</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:12\">ACT 18:12</a></p>",
